Watch how my facial hair has evolved over the years and how I use @braun_global’s new Series 7 both as a tool of self-expression and to manage my desired look on a daily basis! Well-groomed stubble or clean-shaven, whatever look you desire the Series 7 is here to help you #SayItWithAShave

Follow this link (https://bit.ly/3k22n28) to learn more about the Series 7 and comment below with the funniest moment of your shaving journey! Ad

#BraunUK #SayItWithAShave

node.text:
Having breakfast in a cave never looked so good. Tag someone who deserves a vacation here ⬇️

📍The incredible new suites at @acrosuites Crete

#greece #luxuryhotel #travel #cave #drone

CHEST & BACK 🔥

Awesome session today, shifting 3 plates on bench for the first time in a while 💪🏼

1. Flat bench 3x5 + dropset
2. Chest supported row 3x10
3. Incline machine 3x15 into ⬇️
4. Mag-grip pulldown 3x12 + dropset
5. Machine pullover 3x10 into ⬇️
6. Machine fly 3x12
7. Lateral raise 3x12-15

Chest and back will always be my favourite combo 👌🏼 Thanks @tomnealfitness for pushing me through the heavy lifts

Intra workout from @myproteinus

node.text:
Push workout 💪🏼

Can’t go wrong with a bit of chest shoulders and triceps in this great weather

1. DB pause shoulder press 4x10 (dropset)
2. Machine chest press 5x10
3. Cable chest fly 4x12 into ⬇️
4. Kneeling DB lateral 4x12
5. Dips (bodyweight) 4x20-25
6. Tricep rope extensions 4x15/12/10/10

Routine has been a little all over the place since getting to Mallorca but we are still getting it done!

Pre sign up for my APP for an exclusive ongoing discount at launch 👊🏼
